; and synthetic rubber for use in various applications comprising automotive components, hoses, gaskets, rice Dehusking rollers, printing and industrial rollers, friction materials, belting, and footwear. The company was formerly known as Apcotex Lattices Limited and changed its name to Apcotex Industries Limited in 2005. Apcotex Industries Limited was founded in 1980 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}